<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="J" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Jaques" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Jaques,</orth> (dissyll.), name of 1) Saint J. le Grand, whose sanctuary at Florence is resorted to by Helena in <bibl n="shak. aww 3.4.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Alls III, 4, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.5.37" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.5.37" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 37</bibl> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 58</bibl>. 2) J. Falconbridge: <bibl n="shak. lll 2.42" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL II, 42</bibl>. 3) J. Chatillon, admiral of France: H5 III <bibl n="shak. lll 2.5.43" default="NO" valid="yes">5, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.8.98" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 98</bibl>. 4) the melancholy J. in <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 26</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 26</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 26</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 11</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.200" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 200</bibl>. 5) a brother of Oliver and Orlando: <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 5</bibl>. 6) an officer in <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Alls IV, 3, 185</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>